---
title: Beef Meatballs & Garden Salad with Herby Mayo & Onion Chutney
description: For beef meatballs with some Mediterranean vibes, lace them with our rich herb seasoning. Then add an extra layer of flavour by coating them in our onion chutney before serving over a simple and textural salad to balance out the richness. don't forget the drizzle of herby mayo to tie everything together.

*We’ve replaced the creamy pesto dressing in this recipe with dill & parsley mayonnaise due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
